Package algorithm.event

Class GeneticEvent

java.lang.Object
algorithm.event.SimulationEvent
algorithm.event.GeneticEvent
Direct Known Subclasses:
DeathEvent, MutationEvent, ReproductionEvent
public abstract class GeneticEvent extends SimulationEvent
Represents an abstract genetic event in the genetic algorithm. This class provides common functionality for specific genetic events such as death, mutation, and reproduction.
